40|$|We {{consider}} {{an extension of}} Massey's construction of secret sharing schemes using linear codes. We describe the <b>access</b> <b>structure</b> of the scheme and show its connection to the dual code. We use the $g$-fold weight enumerator and invariant theory to study the <b>access</b> <b>structure.</b> Comment: Submitted to ITW 201...|$|R
